des:
Squats Workout is a progressive daily workout designed to help you achieve a superior posterior. And strong quads and core, too.

Each day builds on the previous workout and includes motivational messages to keep you engaged, on track, and disciplined. In no time at all, you'll gain strength, stamina, and an improved bottom line.
